{
  "logNo": "110168916634",
  "title": "양평나들이 1 - 테라로사카페",
  "addDate": "2013. 5. 27.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110168916634",
  "html_size": 194505,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110168916634\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110168916634\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:9pt; font-family:'3028548_9';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">강의나 모임 등 특별한 일정이 없다면</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">주말엔 항상 야외로 나들이 갑니다. </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">애들 엄마가 토요일에도 늦게 까지 일하기에 1박2일은 힘들어서</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">주로 일요일 오전에 떠났다가 저녁에 돌아오는 일정이 되죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이번에는</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">오랫만에 경기도의 동쪽으로 가보기로 합니다. 양평군이 당첨!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">남양주시와 양평군은 제가 공중보건의를 남양주시 조안면에서 근무했었어서 많이 익숙한 곳이죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">(조안면이 양수리에 옆에 있습니다. 강을 사이에 두고 서쪽은 남양주시 조안면, 동쪽은 양평군 서종면)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">첫번째 목표지는</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">카페 '테라로사'입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">커피가 맛있고, 카페가 이쁘다고 유명하더군요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_143/isuhani_1369631184776EaTNz_JPEG/IMG_2051.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_143/isuhani_1369631184776EaTNz_JPEG/IMG_2051.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_143/isuhani_1369631184776EaTNz_JPEG/IMG_2051.JPG?type=w3\"></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">양평 테라로사의 입구입니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">공장으로 들어가는 느낌이죠.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_260/isuhani_1369631207749UMbBW_JPEG/IMG_2115.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_260/isuhani_1369631207749UMbBW_JPEG/IMG_2115.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_260/isuhani_1369631207749UMbBW_JPEG/IMG_2115.JPG?type=w3\"></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>입구 안쪽은 몇개의 건물이 있는데, 갤러리, 베이커리, 교육장, 카페, 정원 등으로 구성되어있더군요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>하얀색 벽이 잘 어울려요</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a82ecda76ed5962.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_116/isuhani_1369631185888H8UHn_JPEG/IMG_2073.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0a82ecda76ed5962.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>카페는 층고가 높고 유리창이 넓어 </p>\r\n<p>밝고 환해서 좋아요. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>여러가지 소품들도 따뜻한 느낌.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>북유럽의 느낌을 재현하고 싶었던 것 같아요 (갤러리나 비치된 책을 통해 유추해본 겁니다)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ac9bb67f3ce946a9.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_201/isuhani_1369631661604U35GE_JPEG/IMG_2060.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ac9bb67f3ce946a9.jpg\"></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>다양한 커피관련 기구와</p>\r\n<p>자루째 있는 커피 원두들.. ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a8bd215beb2b9391.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130527_246/isuhani_1369631185070L2CKM_JPEG/IMG_2066.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/a8bd215beb2b9391.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2층으로 올라가면 북유럽문화관이 있네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>지금은 사진전이 열리고 있었어요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_124/isuhani_1369631661881EK96L_JPEG/IMG_2067.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_124/isuhani_1369631661881EK96L_JPEG/IMG_2067.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_124/isuhani_1369631661881EK96L_JPEG/IMG_2067.JPG?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>아들, 주원이가 </p>\r\n<p>'아빠는 어떤 사진이 좋아요? 나는 이 사진이랑 저 사진이랑이 맘에 들어요'</p>\r\n<p>라면서 신났네요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_121/isuhani_1369631185293O0mfQ_JPEG/IMG_2071.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_121/isuhani_1369631185293O0mfQ_JPEG/IMG_2071.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_121/isuhani_1369631185293O0mfQ_JPEG/IMG_2071.JPG?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>맘에 드는&nbsp;사진 앞에서 사진도 찍어달라고&nbsp;하면서</p>\r\n<p>포즈를 잡네요.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4b6b4d4d376a84f4.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"825\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 1110px\" id=\"20130527_218/isuhani_1369631185582lC14a_JPEG/IMG_2072.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4b6b4d4d376a84f4.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />2층에서 내려오는 계단. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/410ded6b0a46039c.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_196/isuhani_1369631207508Enx3Y_JPEG/IMG_2077.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/410ded6b0a46039c.jpg\"></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />커피와 함께 파스타와 샌드위치, 빵 등을 주문했는데</p>\r\n<p>커피 뿐 아니라</p>\r\n<p>음식도 맛있네요. 재료에도 신경쓴 듯 신선해보이구요.&nbsp;</p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631505283\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631505283\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631505427\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631505427\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631505565\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631505565\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631505779\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631505779\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631506507\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631506507\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631507235\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631507235\">&#65279;</span> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_293/isuhani_1369631186094I4YN9_JPEG/IMG_2103.JPG?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_293/isuhani_1369631186094I4YN9_JPEG/IMG_2103.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130527_293/isuhani_1369631186094I4YN9_JPEG/IMG_2103.JPG?type=w3\"></span></p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631217930\"></span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631217930\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369631218114\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369631218114\">&#65279;</span> \r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">정원 옆 계단으로 내려가면 작은 개울도 있네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">개울을 건너다니면서 노느라 정신 없네요. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">넘어질까 불안불안합니다. 휴~</span></p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8902a3612dcf343b.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_50/isuhani_1369631662240Vefd0_JPEG/IMG_2085.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8902a3612dcf343b.jpg\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>카페 안에서 발견한 풍뎅이를 화분에다 옮겨주고는</p>\r\n<p>유심히 관찰하는 중.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4642dfd8ccb2db92.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_79/isuhani_1369631662878lej2q_JPEG/IMG_2126.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4642dfd8ccb2db92.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>오늘의 테마는 '곤충'</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>풍뎅이에 이어서</p>\r\n<p>송충이를 관찰합니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>냇가와 나무들이 있어서 다양한 벌레들이 있더군요. </p>\r\n<p>각종 벌레들을 관찰하면서 신나하더라구요.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eb5ac698603cbf1b.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_200/isuhani_1369632336096uGNMT_JPEG/IMG_2112.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/eb5ac698603cbf1b.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>빵을 먹으면서 쉬고 있는 딸. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>정원을 가로질러 카페의 건물들이 보입니다. </p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>그곳 테이블에</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>짜잔~~~~</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/efe97d7f1dd140e1.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 740px; rheight: 493px\" id=\"20130527_49/isuhani_1369631662590Qb50y_JPEG/IMG_2120.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A694429A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/efe97d7f1dd140e1.jpg\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span id=\"husky_bookmark_end_1369632396307\">&#65279;</span><span id=\"husky_bookmark_start_1369632396307\">&#65279;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">여배우 이영씨 부부가 어느순간 와 있더군요. ㅎㄷㄷ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">가까이 가서 사진찍긴 좀 쑥스러워서 멀리서 찍었는데도 &nbsp;남다른 분위기를 풍기는게, 역시 톱스타 연예인인가 싶습니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">집사람이 옆에서 해설을 해줍니다. </span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">이영애씨의 집이 이 근처이고, 옆에 남편이고 애들이 어떻고.. 등등...&nbsp; ㅎㅎㅎ</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">테라로사 방문 결론.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">드립커피를 취급하는데, 커피가 맛있더라. (분위기의 영향도 클 것이라 본다)</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">빵도 맛있고, 음식도 맛있더라</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">카페 예쁘더라</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">찾아가기엔 너무 멀다는게 단점이더라. 양평군 서종면 문호리 길가에 있는데, 내비게이션에서 검색이 안되서 주소를 치고 찾아갔네요.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\">여름엔 모기에 주의해야겠더라.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '957317_10'\"></span>&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" />&nbsp;</p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
